# Authorization

This flow is responsible for ensuring the user is authorized to access the system. Any valid user account that authenticates to the system is authorized.


## Data

Authorization data is stored in object `msg.auth` with the following structure.

``` json
{
  "auth": {
    "access": true,
    "user"{
      "username": "barny.gumble",
      "fname": "Barny",
      "lname": "Gumble",
      "mail": "barney.gumble@dinomail.com"
    }
  }
}

```

